bright-iputils (20260520-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian/PPA packaging of the BrightDate iputils fork.
  * Builds b-prefixed networking tools: bping, bclockdiff, btraceroute,
    bmtr, baudit.
  * Adds BrightDate scalar timestamps and BrightSpace spatial extensions.

 -- BrightDate Project <packages@brightdate.org>  Wed, 20 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
